# simple_break_continue_test.geez - Simple Break/Continue test
# This file tests basic break/continue functionality

ማተም "=== Simple Break/Continue Test ==="

# Test 1: Simple Break
ማተም "1. Simple Break Test..."
አስተዋውቅ ቆጠራ = 0
በመሆኑ ቆጠራ < 5 {
    ቆጠራ = ቆጠራ + 1
    ማተም "   Count:" + ቆጠራ
    ከሆነ ቆጠራ == 3 {
        ማተም "   Breaking!"
        ተሰብር
    }
}

# Test 2: Simple Continue
ማተም "2. Simple Continue Test..."
አስተዋውቅ ቆጠራ_2 = 0
በመሆኑ ቆጠራ_2 < 5 {
    ቆጠራ_2 = ቆጠራ_2 + 1
    ከሆነ ቆጠራ_2 == 2 {
        ማተም "   Skipping:" + ቆጠራ_2
        ቀጥል
    }
    ማተም "   Processing:" + ቆጠራ_2
}

# Test 3: Simple For Loop (without break/continue)
ማተም "3. Simple For Loop Test..."
ለ እኔ በ 3 {
    ማተም "   For loop i:" + እኔ
}

ማተም "=== Test Complete ==="
